19:T42d,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a specific size variant (Medium, Right) of an anatomical 3D inguinal hernia mesh system. The brochure description provides strong clinical context: fixation-free, minimally invasive, thermoformed design with sealed edges and orientation markers. Material, specifications, and intended use are unambiguous. However, manufacturer brand verification needed: 'Meril Life Sciences' listed but brand field empty. Product appears to be a specific SKU/variant within FILAPROP 3D Mesh family rather than the family page itself. Size/laterality variants (Medium/Right) suggest this should either be part of a configurator/variant system or merged into parent family page with size selection. No external sources available to verify manufacturer or validate market positioning. Recommend review to: (1) confirm Meril as manufacturer/brand owner, (2) determine if separate pages needed for each size/side combination or if family-level page with variants is more appropriate, (3) verify complete product range within FILAPROP 3D system.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"FILAPROP 3D MESH Medium Right","product_name_display":"FILAPROP 3D MESH Medium Right","sku_code":"PP3D914M-R","product_family":"FILAPROP 3D Mesh","product_family_display":"Filaprop 3D Mesh","slug":"filaprop-3d-mesh-medium-right","images":[{"id":"prop_69c4b9e","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c421263a82b19514dfdfec/cover_46dc714d.jpg","original_filename":"cover_OpulentUni.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":256785,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:06.144704+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1650,"height":2350}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"FILAPROP 3D MESH Medium Right | FILAPROP 3D Mesh Hernia Mesh - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Anatomical 3D mesh for fixation-free minimally invasive inguinal hernia repair. Features unique thermoformed design that conforms to inguinal regio